      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid value for anyone needing a dependable daily commuter. While the engine and transmission are fully functional and the car drives well, prospective buyers should expect some visible wear and tear. There are minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior paint and some staining on the interior upholstery consistent with its age. It has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor maintenance items in the near future to keep it in peak operating condition. Overall, it is a functional, no-frills vehicle ready for the road.",
