      "description": "Available is a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This specimen is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the M-Variable differential lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The individual throttle bodies provide crisp induction response, while the suspension geometry remains perfectly aligned on original-spec bushings. Finished in Carbon Black, the paint depth is exceptional, and the underside remains free of any thermal cycling fatigue or oxidation. A truly turn-key example for the technical purist.",
